name: View at Sarajevo 7 February 2014 during protests in BiH

desc.html: English: View at Sarajevo on 7 February 2014 during 2014 Bosnia and Herzegovina social riots and protests. Dense smoke is caused by the burning several police cars near the building of the state Presidency. The Presidency of Bosnia and Herzegovina was also heavily damaged because the demonstrators set fire to two floors, basement and part archive material of the State Archives of BiH which is located there. Demonstrators also torched and stoned the building of the Centar Municipality, Sarajevo as well as the seat of the regional government of the Sarajevo Canton.
